trans-unit.source: Represents a 2D manipulator at an instant in time.
The unique ID for this manipulator.
The x-coordinate of the manipulator.
The y-coordinate of the manipulator.
Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> object with the specified properties.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 속성을 사용하여 새 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> 개체를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: The x and y parameters must both be a finite number.
trans-unit.target: X 및 y 매개 변수 둘 다 유한 숫자 여야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="x" />-coordinate or <paramref name="y" />-coordinate are <see langword="float.NaN" />, <see langword="float.PositiveInfinity" />, or <see langword="float.NegativeInfinity" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="x" />-좌표 또는 <paramref name="y" />-좌표는 <see langword="float.NaN" />, <see langword="float.PositiveInfinity" /> 또는 <see langword="float.NegativeInfinity" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: These values are all invalid.
trans-unit.target: 이러한 값은 모두 사용할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> object to compare this object to.

Determines whether this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> object has the same value as the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" />개체가 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> 개체와 같은 값을 가지는지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulator2D" /> objects are the same type and represent the same value; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
